/* FRAMEWORK */

Create (Creating)
Build learning resources, from scratch or by remixing existing materials.

Connect (Connecting)
Communicate with students in real time or asynchronously. 

Collaborate (Collaborating)
A platform for collaboration and co-creation.

Curate (Curating)
Collect, organise and share content. 

Capture (Capturing)
Record an event, activity or artefact.

Captivate (Captivating)
Create interactive learning opportunities that engage.

Check (Checking)
Gauge students understanding.

